收<br />\n抵撚死"},{"pid":"875ac6b49e3ae2d36dc239affd7f38f326a8f834","tid":1901104,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:28:36.000Z","msg":"英文source: <a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/coronavirus-iran-vice-president-masoumeh-ebtekar-test-positive-outbreak-latest-a9363181.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fcoronavirus-iran-vice-president-masoumeh-ebtekar-test-positive-outbreak-latest-a9363181.html&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0fsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=98504ab3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/coronavirus-iran-vice-president-masoumeh-ebtekar-test-positive-outbreak-latest-a9363181.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Coronavirus: Iran's vice-president diagnosed with disease as outbreak spreads</strong><br />\n<br />\nIran&rsquo;s vice-president has been diagnosed with coronavirus, state media have reported, as the country struggles to stop the spread of the disease.<br />\n<br />\nMasoumeh Ebtekar is among 254 people infected with the virus in the Middle Eastern nation, where 26 people have been killed.<br />\n<br />\nThe vice-president for women and family affairs is better known internationally as the English-language spokeswoman for the hostage-takers who seized the US embassy in Tehran in 1979, sparking a 444-day diplomatic crisis.<br />\n<br />\nIran&rsquo;s deputy health minister tested positive for the virus earlier this week, hours after appearing visibly unwell at a press conference during which he denied the government was suppressing the scale of the outbreak.<br />\n<br />\nCoronavirus cases in Iran spiked by 106 over the last 24 hours, the country&rsquo;s health ministry announced on Thursday. The country&rsquo;s death toll from the outbreak is higher than any country except China, where the epidemic began.<br />\n<br />\nThe outbreak has prompted Iranian authorities to cancel Friday prayers in Tehran. Health ministry spokesman Kianush Jahanpur said there were also plans to impose restrictions at some holy Muslim sites but the plan &ldquo;needs the approval of the president before being carried out&rdquo;."},{"pid":"7f410d9634a184299e95a42f8c729fa5d00aa543","tid":1901104,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"美國一直為人類文明作出貢獻<br />\n中國一直破壞人類文明<br />\n武漢肺炎完全展示出中國既成績<br />\n不費一卒已經玩殘各國"},{"pid":"30ded2d7f530dd6194d7185bf8e60dcb8c834cf4","tid":1901104,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"滅國未"},{"pid":"c8ec16ccd3309e176296f505cabac090067c66e4","tid":1901104,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76fcdef1052a27422e5999ccee21c7056fcb26fd","tid":1901104,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"當年啲暴徒<br />\n家陣比天收<br />\n抵撚死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"幾時收林奠?"},{"pid":"972acce9fede783200e7a089f78d5b24ee3fda80","tid":1901104,"uid":255269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:36:56.000Z","msg":"鍾南山仲好意思話病毒唔係出自中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cce83eb9b854494a5a9a1260ea157420da8c84","tid":1901104,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xpea99m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxpea99m.jpg&h=4a4d5dde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee7c06f32375074d1e89d588e4ba2f2035bfbfb3","tid":1901104,"uid":237962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76fcdef1052a27422e5999ccee21c7056fcb26fd","tid":1901104,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"當年啲暴徒<br />\n家陣比天收<br />\n抵撚死"},"cited